comments: Carter Jr. (ORL) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Wagner (ORL) legally contests Ingram's (NOP) jump shot attempt.
Wagner (ORL) is moving alongside Ingram's (NOP) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the drive.
Ingram (NOP) extends his arm and delivers contact that dislodges Wagner (ORL) from his legally obtained defensive position.
Banchero (ORL) and Richardson (NOP) come together at the same spot and marginal contact occurs as the defender switch.
Richardson (NOP) makes clean contact with the ball as he defends Banchero's (ORL) shot in the lane.
Wagner (ORL) is moving alongside Ingram's (NOP) path and marginal contact occurs on the drive.
Wagner (ORL) and Ingram (NOP) come together at the same spot and marginal contact occurs at the start of the drive.
Carter Jr. (ORL) maintains verticality and absorbs the contact that occurs during Jones' (NOP) layup attempt.
Jones (NOP) extends his left arm out and initiates contact with Banchero's (ORL) face, which affects his ability to pursue the rebound.
Jones (NOP) and Carter Jr. (ORL) briefly engage and disengage as they pursue the rebound.
McCollum (NOP) makes clean contact with the ball as he tries to dislodge it from Banchero (ORL).
McCollum (NOP) legally contests Wagner's (ORL) shot attempt.
Wagner (ORL) brings his hands forward towards Ingram's (NOP) path and marginal contact occurs as they disengage during the inbound.
Richardson (NOP) takes more than five seconds to inbound the ball.
Carter Jr. (ORL) legally contests Ingram's (NOP) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
McCollum (NOP) commits a take foul on Fultz (ORL).
Richardson (NOP) commits a take foul on Banchero (ORL).
